    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强烈推荐使用手柄游玩！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/057b7e0f278e09580efef49807ff4a2a.poster.avif?t=1756162685\" width=480 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/057b7e0f278e09580efef49807ff4a2a.webm?t=1756162685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/057b7e0f278e09580efef49807ff4a2a.mp4?t=1756162685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是诡秘混沌之神Skoroz的变形信徒。在猎巫狂潮中，你的族人惨遭屠戮，如今你孤身一人——Skoroz的信徒非死即囚，或杳无踪迹。神力衰微，强敌环伺，你是这位暴怒神祇复仇计划的最后希望。面对举国围剿，你必须在饥荒、瘟疫与战火肆虐的Avencia王国中探索、隐匿、战斗，在这濒临崩溃的中世纪世界杀出血路。身负混沌之神的禁忌恩赐，你能否颠覆人类王国？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/0ce46f10623612f2dfc0df706c42d9bc.poster.avif?t=1756162685\" width=480 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/0ce46f10623612f2dfc0df706c42d9bc.webm?t=1756162685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/0ce46f10623612f2dfc0df706c42d9bc.mp4?t=1756162685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏背景设定在暴乱、内战与迷信交织的中世纪世界。随着多方势力争夺Avencia王国的控制权，制造混乱与毁灭的契机已在你掌握中。然而巨额悬赏令让追兵如潮水般涌来敌人，一旦暴露行踪，无数对你展开不死不休的追猎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/3835a305ad9f068cc377502258688a64.poster.avif?t=1756162685\" width=480 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/3835a305ad9f068cc377502258688a64.webm?t=1756162685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/3835a305ad9f068cc377502258688a64.mp4?t=1756162685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >囚徒掌握着多种致命变形能力。强力的战斗技能，隐蔽潜行和变形可供玩家随意制定策略。陷入穷途末路时，囚徒的终极技能可以化身为拥有可怕力量的怪物，足以摧毁整个军队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/ee04d18f1e6ceee3e874c54c1e519b86.poster.avif?t=1756162685\" width=480 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/ee04d18f1e6ceee3e874c54c1e519b86.webm?t=1756162685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166890/extras/ee04d18f1e6ceee3e874c54c1e519b86.mp4?t=1756162685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Necrofugitive》的敌人搭载反应式AI系统——每名士兵拥有独特的性格特质，使其拥有不同的战斗决策。他们不会无脑冲锋送死，而是能识别危险并撤退、组建防御阵型、策划伏击，甚至听从指挥官调度。你的敌人会不断研究你的战斗模式：缠斗越久，他们就越能洞悉你的攻击方式，进而制定反制策略。唯有灵活运用多样化的技能组合，才能让敌人难以预测你的行动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Necrofugitive》通过手绘动画与动态光照效果生动呈现Avencia世界——从坍塌的地牢到日影斑驳的森林，每个场景都力求还原中世纪的真实质感。游戏灵感源自中世纪的多重危机，力求打造鲜活角色与沉浸环境，让你以传说中肆虐巨兽的视角，亲历文明崩坏前的最后癫狂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
